<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA63">
<l>ēṟēḻum veṉṟaṭartta ventai yeriyuruvat</l>
<l>tēṟēṟip paṭṭa viṭucāpam – pāṟēṟi</l>
<l>yuṇṭatalai vāyniṟaiyak kōṭṭaṅkai yoṇkuruti</l>
<l>kaṇṭaporuḷ colliṟ katai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When speaking about the meaning that is seen, [there is] the story</l>
<l>of the release of the curse to which the flame-shaped bull rider  had fallen,</l>
<l>[and] of the bright blood in the curved palm, when our Father, who had vanquished [and] killed seven bulls,</l>
<l>filled the opening of the skull mounted [and] eaten by vultures.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
